e slowly and rest for a minute.                                                                                                                                                           game meaning play rules                                                                                                                                         Game meaning                                                    A game is play with rules.                                                                                                                                                                      rest meaning time recover                                                                                                                                       Rest meaning                                                    Rest is time to recover.                                                                                                                                                                        unusual demo but real                                                                                                                                           Unusual demo                                                    It is unusual, but it is real.                                                                                                                                                                  mistake recovery recover bad answer wrong ask shorter question switch packs give exact error                                                                    Mistake recovery                                                If an answer is wrong, ask a shorter question, switch packs, or give the exact error.                                                                                                           release proof useful includes tests checksums logs asset names final tag target                                                                       